FBIS4-68268 "jpuma019___94022" JPRS-UMA-94-019 JPRS Central Eurasia Military Affairs 19 April 1994 GENERAL ISSUES ARMS TRADE Vladimir Arms Show Planned for Late May Vladimir Arms Show Planned for Late May 944D0017B Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 19 Apr 94 p 1 944D0017B Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA Russian CSO [Rosvooruzheniye State Company Press Service article under the "Novosti" rubric: "Russian Arms Exhibition"] [Text] An exhibition (to be held from 24 to 28 May) will include about 30 enterprises of the Russian VPK [military-industrial complex], which will display small arms, rocket and artillery weapons, PVO [air defense] items, and engineer equipment. The exhibition is being organized by the Golden Gates of Russia Vladimir-Suzdal International Fair AO [joint-stock company]. Visitors will be able to speak with representatives of the Rosvooruzheniye State Company and discuss purchasing of weapons and military equipment.
